  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd3\u0d9d\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dd3 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One of the two elephants was killed by a power line",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An elephant has died due to electric shock in Dighavapi Pallachena area of \u200b\u200bAkkarapattua police area of \u200b\u200bAmpara district. A resident of this village has put up these illegal power lines to protect his land. The elephant that was roaming in this area at night has died after hitting this power line.",
        "According to the wildlife officials, the height of the dead elephant is seven feet and four inches and the animal is about 10 years old. Later, the guard of the land was arrested and the owner of the land was presented to the Magistrate. The owner of the land is being arrested.",
        "Wildlife officials state that two elephants roam around Dighavapi and one of them has died.",
        "It is also said that the veterinarian Nihal Pushpakumara of the Ampara Wildlife Health Unit is currently conducting the post-mortem examination of this elephant.",
        "On the advice of Eastern Province Wildlife Assistant Director Mr. Prasantha Wimaladasa, a group including Ampara Wildlife Site Guard Mr. Kitsiri Mevan are conducting further investigations."
      ],
